    "content": "* Comms: Assuming budget change goes through, new website launch anticipated for end of january, will need help from various team members, will reach out\n* Office Hours Guests - President\n* Eric: Starting next semester we will limit to only 1 friend / non-officer while in the office  (esp if it’s not your OH). As we become a larger and more active team, it is difficult to work in a busy environment that has become almost too welcoming to outsiders.",
